cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.PL 

The paper proposes a new approach for generative modeling that incorporates programs representing global structure into the model. This involves leveraging program synthesis to generate training data. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision)
- cs.SY (Systems and Control)
- cs.PL (Programming Languages)
